"We're here!" Terrorsaur shouted down to the two Predacon wolves. He flew 
down to the entrance of the cave, then transformed to robot mode, taking a 
careful check of the situation. There was a new smell here. A few new smell. 
He took a check of the bots inside. He even looked for Megatron, hearing he 
wasn't in a good mood.
